[vc_row overlay_dotted="" css=".vc_custom_1544444590874{padding-top: 9% !important;padding-bottom: 1% !important;}"][vc_column][havnor_section_title title_text="Popular Questions" content_text="Then one day he was shooting at some food and up through the ground came a bubbling crude to the east side to a deluxe apartment in the sky." btm_space="40px"][vc_accordion accordion_style="style-two" one_active="true" active_tab="1"][vc_accordion_tab title="How do I earn points?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540619936351{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"]Let your server know you are a member of the rewards program and provide your phone number. Using your restaurant's table top tablet, you can enter your phone number to earn points for your visit. Earn 1 point for every 1 dollar spent on eligible items. You can also earn points for delivery, ToGo and catering orders, where applicable. Certain items are not eligible to earn points such as gift cards, merchandise, tax and gratuity or charitable items. Earning points on alcohol is subject to state and location laws and varies by location.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="What information do I give the restaurant to locate my account?" sub_title="Sub Title 2"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540619957577{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"]All you need to give them is your mobile phone number[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Can I earn points on catering, online orders, ToGo orders and private dining?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540619987802{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"]Yes, you can. You will earn 1 point for every 1 dollar spent for your catering, online and ToGo orders. You will earn ½ point for every 1 dollar spent for your private and group dining transactions at select brands.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Do my points or rewards expire?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540620009686{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"]Points expire only if there are no purchases (whether with dollars, rewards points or reward certificates) within a 120 day period. Reward certificates will be valid through the expiration date specified on the reward.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="What type of rewards can I redeem points for?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540620030320{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"]You can redeem your points for a variety of items. You can redeem for Reward Certificates in denominations of $10, $25 and $50 off at all participating restaurants. You can also redeem your points for a variety of items such as free appetizers, entrées, desserts, and more. Be sure to check back as we may add new rewards.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Where do I find my current point balance?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540620080858{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"]You can find your current points balance and available rewards by signing into your rewards account on your restaurants tabletop tablet or by viewing the upper right-hand corner of the website by simply logging in at www.havnor.com/customer-service/account-login and then navigating to www.havnor.com/customer-service/my-rewards.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row_content" equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle" overlay_dotted="" css=".vc_custom_1542959147276{padding-top: 10% !important;}"][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1534156862831{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}" offset="vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-12 vc_col-xs-12"][vc_single_image img_size="full" css=".vc_custom_1545218562741{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"][/vc_column][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1534156868484{padding-top: 3px !important;background-color: #1c1f26 !important;}" offset="vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-12 vc_col-xs-12"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1533967073524{padding-right: 5% !important;padding-left: 15% !important;}"][hanor_services stunnhing_services="" open_link="true" image_icon="icon-tab" service_icon="pe-7s-search" service_title="url:%230|title:Tasty%20Foods||" title_color="#ffffff" content_color="#ffffff" service_btm="0px" service_item_btm="0px"]SEO is most important part to run a successful business. Organic searches only stays as lifetime.[/hanor_services][hanor_services stunnhing_services="" open_link="true" image_icon="icon-tab" service_icon="icon-speedometer" service_title="url:%230|title:Lovely%20Service||" title_color="#ffffff" content_color="#ffffff" service_top="0px" service_item_top="0px"]We constantly hear your feedbacks that you get better a experience while you’re using our WordPress themes.[/hanor_services][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1533967078955{padding-right: 15% !important;padding-left: 5% !important;}"][hanor_services stunnhing_services="" open_link="true" image_icon="icon-tab" service_icon="pe-7s-monitor" service_title="url:%230|title:Special%20Drinks||" title_color="#ffffff" content_color="#ffffff" service_btm="0px" service_item_btm="0px"]Having these multiple page designs, The site will adapt &amp; comfortably work in any type of device .[/hanor_services][hanor_services stunnhing_services="" open_link="true" image_icon="icon-tab" service_icon="icon-expand" service_title="url:%230|title:Table%20Ordering||" title_color="#ffffff" content_color="#ffffff" service_top="0px" service_item_top="0px"]Take your business further with flexible credit and reward programs, and floorplan and leasing options.[/hanor_services][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" overlay_dotted="" css=".vc_custom_1544422701953{padding-top: 6% !important;background-color: #f9f9f9 !important;}"][vc_column][havnor_section_title title_text="General Questions" content_text="Find a short list of our most frequently asked questions." btm_space="50px"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" overlay_dotted="" css=".vc_custom_1544422509068{padding-bottom: 8% !important;background-color: #f9f9f9 !important;}"][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1530614708280{padding-top: 0px !important;}" offset="vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-12"][vc_accordion one_active="true" active_tab="2"][vc_accordion_tab title="What are the hours of operation for Havnor?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540619628662{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"]Havnor hours vary by location. Please find your nearest restaurant to see hours of operation. Lunch is served Monday through Friday until 3pm. Our practice is to serve our dinner menu all day on Saturdays, Sundays, and holidays. As a courtesy to guests who ask, we will provide a lunch menu at any time. There are some regional variations.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Holiday Hours" sub_title="Sub Title 2"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540619664262{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"]Havnor restaurants are closed on Thanksgiving Day and Christmas Day to allow our team members to spend time with their family and friends. Depending on the amount of business on the day before these holidays, the restaurants may close early. We leave this decision to the discretion of the management team. Please contact the restaurant directly for the scheduled closing time the day before Thanksgiving or Christmas Eve.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="What is the current promotion? Are there any specials?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540619688918{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"]To be the first to find out about promotions, specials, and news sign up to our eClub Opens a New Window. ! You can also check out our Specials Page for current offers![/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Where will you be building future Havnor restaurants?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540619755566{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"]Check out our future Olive Havnor restaurants. These are updated constantly, so check anytime for the latest information. Actual locations and opening dates are subject to change. If your city is not listed, we hope to be coming soon![/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Where do I fill out a survey of my visit?"][vc_column_text]You may take a brief survey on our Ziosk tableside tablet after your meal. For takeout orders and at our Canadian restaurants, there is a unique code on your receipt which is needed in order to complete a survey.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1530614727224{padding-top: 0px !important;}" offset="vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-12"][vc_accordion one_active="true" active_tab="4"][vc_accordion_tab title="Where can I get a coupon?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540619795724{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"]Sign up for our eClub Opens a New Window. and Fan us on Facebook Opens a New Window. to receive info about our specials and coupons. Don't forget to check your metropolitan-area newspapers for offers![/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Do you give back to local organizations?" sub_title="Sub Title 2"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540619814112{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"]As we look for ways to give back to our guests, investing in our communities is one of the best investments we can make. Our restaurants serve their communities through a variety of local efforts.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Do you offer group discounts?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540619836430{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"]Rather than offer a discount to one particular group of guests, we believe our responsibility is to make sure we're providing the best dining value possible to every guest who joins us for lunch or dinner.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Is there a free birthday offer in the restaurant?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540619869493{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"]Havnor guests can receive a complimentary dessert on their birthday when they dine with us. To receive other great offers, simply sign up for our eClub Opens a New Window. and be sure to include information like your birthdate and address so we can keep you updated on the latest Havnor news and send you special coupons for your local Havnor.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Will servers sing Happy Birthday?"][vc_column_text]Thank you for considering us for your celebrations! Our team members would be happy to join your group in singing Happy Birthday to the guest of honor.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]
